data.description: BRING ALL OFFERS! SELLER WILL ASSIST IN A RATE BUY DOWN TO AS LOW AS 4.99% USING SELLERS PREFERRED LENDER OR HELP WITH CLOSING COSTS! This home is sitting on a +/- third of an acre cul-de-sac lot in the Forest creek neighborhood, and Round Rock ISD.  This is a unique opportunity to own a beautiful 11 year young home with a than 2 year old refreshing pool. You will want to step outback on on your custom screened-in patio, so to relax, grab a book, and listen to the birds and the wonderful sounds of nature. An extraordinary outdoor living space, it’s a backyard oasis. Enjoy your morning coffee, or dine al fresco. Your future home offers 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, and 1 half bath, a large 3 car garage, with plenty of additional storage. When it comes to playtime or entertaining, this home offers you an abundance of living space. There are 2 large living areas that include a game room up, and an oversized living room down that is pre-wired for surround sound. You have 2 additional flex spaces that can be used as a formal dining, formal living room, library, sitting room, or an office. Open to the family room is your nice size entertainer kitchen. With the adjacent in kitchen dining area, and breakfast bar makes this the perfect home for small or large birthdays, pool parties, and holiday gatherings. This carefully maintained home has a new water softener, and recent rain gutters with leaf guards. The downstairs master bedroom offers an abundance of light, and tile floor. As you enter the master bath you notice right away the dual vanities, a separate shower, and a jetted garden tub with a large walk-in closet. All other bedrooms are upstairs that includes a separate in-law/guest suite with a full bath attached. All upstairs bedrooms are of nice size with walk-in closets. You will be close to many of the major employers, grocery stores, and just minutes to all toll roads and highways. Too much to list here, so much home for you to love, you have to see it before it’s gone!
